      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="24557762">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1076366/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1076366-2.jpg" alt="han" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/24557762/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/24557762/" class="">第1页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1076366/" class=" " title="han">han</a>
                (千卷蠹书忘岁月 一杯浊酒信乾坤)
              
                <span class="allstar40" title="推荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="24557762">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">清末民初思想界要求尽破伦理结构的束缚以便急速动员全国力量，自然是受了国难的刺激，但是这一脉思想对后来中国命运的发展起了不小影响。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2013-02-13 22:52</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                清末民初思想界要求尽破伦理结构的束缚以便急速动员全国力量，自然是受了国难的刺激，但是这一脉思想对后来中国命运的发展起了不小影响。
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







